opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 15th day of December, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the “Affidavit,” and the Application to Expedite are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
